ing: 1 (10.75 ounce) can condensed cream of mushroom soup
des: "Great for leftover ham. This is easy to make with ingredients you probably already have in the kitchen. Try adding peas or other vegetables, if desired."
ins:
Preheat oven to 375 degrees F (190 degrees C).
Place the noodles, ham, cheese, soup and milk in a 9x9 inch casserole dish and mix well.
Bake at 375 degrees F (190 degrees C) for 25 to 30 minutes.
